{"tid":1915824,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔兔大眼睛&大耳朵的構造用來偵測敵人追食 :D","createTime":"2020-03-08T13:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T08:19:09.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45427645e9b2943c68414f706564b688168ff32d","tid":1915824,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"兔子大眼睛和大耳朵的構造令牠們在大自然內容易偵測到被補獵者追食。因為眼睛範圍大，<span style=\"color: gold;\">你在牠後面也會看到你</span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\">側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</span>。牠們<span style=\"color: gold;\">正前方和下方是盲點</span>，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">所以有時食物在牠下巴下面看不到</span>)。&nbsp;兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你一直是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9ptBVt-J2zU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9ptBVt-J2zU&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=a27a6229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9ptBVt-J2zU</a>"},{"pid":"f791497fa5a0711452bcaf495c5c80d4431661c8","tid":1915824,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5c356fdc05fb5936b00c7e9b2a1b00d54ec2f9","tid":1915824,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647d7d7b28a0c683339e929b59f2c38f4d738ca7","tid":1915824,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3784a99c4e5917584cb0b397a290e7c316cdacf0","tid":1915824,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48af6645365979c439285c9d53bf896a08433b3c","tid":1915824,"uid":295477,"like":0,"